#****f* extelem.tcl/extelem.netlayer
# NAME
#   extelem.netlayer -- layer
# SYNOPSIS
#   set layer [extelem.netlayer]
# FUNCTION
#   Returns the layer on which the extelem operates, i.e. returns LINK.
